            "title": "全民國家安全教育日│海關國安物品X光機 一眼睇穿可疑物品",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/51fabe5b4757f5e4db39af47966a02d8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040912013392581.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>本月15日是「全民國家安全教育日」，保安局轄下部門之中，繼警務處打頭陣介紹國家安全物品後，消防處、入境處亦分別介紹其國安物品，今日(9日)第四日來到香港海關登場，作為守護國家南大門的把關者，部門最重要國安物品便是X光機，可以一眼睇穿可疑物品。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4184999/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關Ｘ光機一眼睇穿可疑物品。保安局fb  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef3c6f36504b3b2075380a1c0ac87ba9/2025-04/20.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關Ｘ光機一眼睇穿可疑物品。保安局fb  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185000/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7d533880a3dcba2a39f3893c204348f/2025-04/21_3.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185001/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"智慧車底機械人進行清關工作。保安局fb  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ff551c93a71fadf5732a83793e0738a6/2025-04/22_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        智慧車底機械人進行清關工作。保安局fb  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185002/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關Ｘ光機一眼睇穿可疑物品。保安局fb  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/46c4900ff068388ca693b06f26377574/2025-04/23_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關Ｘ光機一眼睇穿可疑物品。保安局fb  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>今日保安局在社交平台facebook發布影片，講解海關的國安物品，指海關一直致力維護國家安全，日常工作涉及守護國家的國土安全、經濟安全、社會安全，以及生態安全等範疇，國安物品便是一台Ｘ光機，不單止是海關維護國家安全工作上重要夥伴，更象徵著海關持續運用，各類型高科技儀器，進行日常客運及貨運的清關工作，堅決打擊及堵截一切危害國家安全的物品流入香港，守護國家的南大門。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062953/即時-港聞-全民國家安全教育日│海關國安物品X光機-一眼睇穿可疑物品",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 12:07:01",
